PHProjekt - README

Manual installation and update: please read the "INSTALL" file
or the wiki documentation.
(http://docs.phprojekt.com/index.php/Administrator:Manual_installation)

Automatic installation: read wiki documentation.
(http://docs.phprojekt.com/index.php/Administrator:Automatic_installation)

Version 6.0.0 - 2010-03-18
