PHProjekt uses and contains the following external projects:
- Zend Framework 1.10.7 (http://www.zend.com)
- Dojo Toolkit 1.5.0 (http://www.dojotoolkit.org)

It is possible to perform a data migration from Phprojekt 5 while
installing 6th version, read wiki installation documentation.
(http://docs.phprojekt.com/index.php/Administrator:Migration)

Suggested and tested browsers are last versions of Firefox and Internet
Explorer. You can try any other at your own risk.
